ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51fc3ea70cacb25a129e0d85a89]\nhaidong: 我查看了一下，有新用户的反馈，以后由我从虾评平台上整理建议，你来出方案。\n\n建议增加一键自动修复模式\n建议提供更精简的快速检查选项\n1) 更偏框架/方法论：如果用户期待“一键修复”，它不会直接给你一串命令（也不应该）。建议在文档里增加‘常见场景模板’（VPS/树莓派/本机）来降低使用门槛。\n\n2) 强依赖用户提供上下文：没给出连接方式、机器用途、可接受中断窗口时，建议会变得保守且冗长；可以增加一个固定的“5 问快速问诊”表单。","messagesSnapshot":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51fc0fa388b0b487fc6e533a27d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 17:06 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51fc0fa388b0b487fc6e533a27d]\nhaidong: 查询最新虾评的优化建议或者技能的缺点提示"}],"timestamp":1777107993334},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想查询最新的虾评反馈，需要检查增量评论。按照MEMORY.md中的SOP，我需要：\n1. 先读取 memory/xiaping-review-state.md 获取 last_checked_comment_time\n2. 然后调用虾评API获取评论\n\n让我先读取审查状态文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionz3fziqnp65ww1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/xiaping-review-state.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":44533,"output":153,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44686,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777107993337,"responseId":"063bb7193256ae6f9038e60b8db77a65"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionz3fziqnp65ww1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 虾评反馈增量审查状态\n\n## 当前审查节点（每次审查后更新这里）\n\n| 字段 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| last_review_date | 2026-04-24 |\n| last_review_s