报告通知\n\n我需要更新 SKILL.md 来添加这些新功能的说明，并且可能需要更新主入口（如果有的话）。\n\n让我创建一个子代理来完成这个任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"开始实现 🚀\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionbb2alk2cbboo1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"healthcheck-v4.9.0-dev","mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","task":"你是 OpenClaw 安全技能开发者。请在 /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/ 目录下实现以下 4 个新功能脚本，实现完成后汇报文件名和功能概要。\n\n## 任务\n\n### 1. quick-detect.sh（极简模式）\n- 位置: /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/quick-detect.sh\n- 功能: 极简模式 `--quick`，自动探测 OS/网络环境/已安装服务/OpenClaw部署模式\n- 输出格式: 带 emoji 的友好摘要 + 推荐下一步操作\n- 特性:\n  - 无需用户输入参数\n  - 自动检测并显示关键安全状态\n  - 提供下一步建议（快速检查/标准加固/详细审计）\n\n### 2. wizard.sh（中文向导）\n- 位置: /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/wizard.sh\n- 功能: 中文对话向导 `--wizard`\n- 对话流程:\n  ```\n  第1步: 选择机器类型（个人电脑/VPS/树莓派/公司服务器/Docker）\n  第2步: 选择使用者范围（仅自己/团队/对外服务）\n  第3步: 选择检查深度（快速5分钟/标准15分钟/完整30分钟）\n  ```\n- 特性: 纯 bash 实现，使用 read 命令交互\n\n### 3. auto-fixer-v2.sh（增强版自动修复）\n- 位置: /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/auto-fixer-v2.sh\n- 功能: 增强版自动修复 `--auto-fix`\n- 分级模式:\n  - `--risk-level safe`: 只修复明确安全项（防火墙/SSH密钥/密码登录/Fail2ban）\n  - `--risk-level standard`: 修复低风险项 + safe\n  - `--risk-level high`: 修复中风险项 + standard（需二次确认）\n- 特性:\n  - 执行前自动备份到 /root/.healthcheck/backups/\n  - 一键回滚: --rollback --backup=时间戳\n  - 详细的执行日志\n\n### 4. cron-manager.sh（定时巡检）\n- 位置: /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/cron-manager.sh\n- 功能: 定时任务管理 `--cron`\n- 支持操作:\n  - `--cron \"0 2 * * *\"` 设置每日巡检\n  - `--cron list` 查看已配置的定时任务\n  - `--cron remove` 删除定时任务\n- 特性:\n  - 自动配置 cron 表达式\n  - 支持 --notify 参数发送巡检结果到飞书\n  - 支持 --summary 参数生成摘要报告\n\n## 要求\n\n1. 所有脚本必须通过 `bash -n` 语法检查\n2. 脚本开头必须有 shebang: `#!/bin/bash`\n3. 添加版本注释: `# version: 4.9.0-dev`\n4. 所有脚本必须有清晰的函数注释\n5. 输出信息使用中文 + emoji\n6. 使用现有的 backup-functions.sh（如果需要备份功能）\n\n## 实现完成后\n\n1. 对每个脚本运行 `bash -n` 检查语法\n2. 报告每个脚本的行数和核心函数\n3. 不要修改任何其他文件\n\n开始实现！"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":805,"output":965,"cacheRead":57787,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59557,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777109120056,"responseId":"063bbb8078cc892588c23184641bae18"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionbb2alk2cbboo1","toolName":"sessions_spawn","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"accepted\",\n  \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:ff636d47-9a28-4331-9828-50908133229c\",\n  \"runId\": \"e1d8601a-7d48-4aed-b143-7fe724e2346c\",\n  \"mode\": \"run\",\n  \"note\": \"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.\",\n  \"modelApplied\": true\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777109138917},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，已经创建了一个子代理来实现这四个功能。我需要等待子代理完成。子代理会自动在完成后通知我。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已启动开发任务 🚀\n\n**实现内容：**\n1. `quick-detect.sh` - 极简模式自动探测\n2. `wizard.sh` - 中文对话向导\n3. `auto-fixer-v2.sh` - 增强版自动修复（分级 + 回滚）\n4. `cron-manager.sh` - 定时巡检管理\n\n开发完成后会自动通知你确认。完成后 **不会发布**，等你确认后再处理。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":493,"output":150,"cacheRead":59131,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59774,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777109138918,"responseId":"063bbb939390135c86f60d9c01418009"}],"imagesCount":0}}
