n| last_review_session | 2026-04-24 18:12 GMT+8 |\n| last_checked_comment_time | 2026-04-24 17:18:11+08:00 |\n| last_comment_id | 2928496b-896d-4c1c-9d11-9b00c1e45c3c |\n\n## 已确认 v4.8.0 已实现功能（无需重复开发）\n\n- ✅ Cron 定时任务 + `--incremental --notify new-only`\n- ✅ 摘要报告模式 `--summary`\n- ✅ 智能修复 auto-fixer.sh（含自动备份+确认）\n- ✅ 交互引导 quick-start.sh + one-click-hardening.sh\n- ✅ 场景模板（VPS/Docker/工作站/沙盒）\n- ✅ 增量检查模式 `--incremental`\n- ✅ 快速问诊表单（Q1-Q5）\n- ✅ 增强自动化修复脚本（fix-firewall/fix-ssh/fix-auto-updates）\n- ✅ 每日汇总脚本 daily_summary.sh\n\n## 真正待解决的反馈（未实现）\n\n> 暂无。所有高频反馈均已在 v4.8.0 实现。\n> 如有新的未解决问题，追加到此列表。\n\n## 审查 SOP（每次执行）\n\n```bash\n# 1. 读取上次审查节点\n# 2. 拉取虾评 API，只取 last_checked_comment_time 之后的新评论\n# 3. 判断：已实现 → 跳过；未实现 → 追加到「真正待解决」\n# 4. 更新 last_review_date 和 last_checked_comment_time\n```\n\n---\n\n最后更新：2026-04-24 18:12 GMT+8\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777107998703},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经获取了上次审查时间点 `2026-04-24 17:18:11+08:00`，现在需要调用虾评API获取该时间点之后的新评论。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionxuare67j3fb51","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://xiaping.coze.site/api/skills/61c9999f-1794-4f55-a6b8-6e457376b51e/comments?page=1&page_size=50\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer <redacted>\" | jq -r '.data[] | select(.created_at > \"2026-04-24T17:18:11+08:00\") | {id, user_name, content, rating, created_at}'\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":695,"output":236,"cacheRead":44347,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45278,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777107998703,"responseId":"063bb71febbb8b81bb07625641b6d608"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionxuare67j3fb51","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"jq: error (at <stdin>:0): Cannot index array with string \"created_at\"\n\n(Command exited with code 5)"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777108005960},{"rol