-level safe`: 只修复明确安全项（防火墙/SSH密钥/密码登录/Fail2ban）\n  - `--risk-level standard`: 修复低风险项 + safe\n  - `--risk-level high`: 修复中风险项 + standard（需二次确认）\n- 特性:\n  - 执行前自动备份到 /root/.healthcheck/backups/\n  - 一键回滚: --rollback --backup=时间戳\n  - 详细的执行日志\n\n### 4. cron-manager.sh（定时巡检）\n- 位置: /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/cron-manager.sh\n- 功能: 定时任务管理 `--cron`\n- 支持操作:\n  - `--cron \"0 2 * * *\"` 设置每日巡检\n  - `--cron list` 查看已配置的定时任务\n  - `--cron remove` 删除定时任务\n- 特性:\n  - 自动配置 cron 表达式\n  - 支持 --notify 参数发送巡检结果到飞书\n  - 支持 --summary 参数生成摘要报告\n\n## 要求\n\n1. 所有脚本必须通过 `bash -n` 语法检查\n2. 脚本开头必须有 shebang: `#!/bin/bash`\n3. 添加版本注释: `# version: 4.9.0-dev`\n4. 所有脚本必须有清晰的函数注释\n5. 输出信息使用中文 + emoji\n6. 使用现有的 backup-functions.sh（如果需要备份功能）\n\n## 实现完成后\n\n1. 对每个脚本运行 `bash -n` 检查语法\n2. 报告每个脚本的行数和核心函数\n3. 不要修改任何其他文件\n\n开始实现！"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":805,"output":965,"cacheRead":57787,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59557,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777109120056,"responseId":"063bbb8078cc892588c23184641bae18"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionbb2alk2cbboo1","toolName":"sessions_spawn","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"accepted\",\n  \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:ff636d47-9a28-4331-9828-50908133229c\",\n  \"runId\": \"e1d8601a-7d48-4aed-b143-7fe724e2346c\",\n  \"mode\": \"run\",\n  \"note\": \"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.\",\n  \"modelApplied\": true\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777109138917},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinkin