强 | Enhanced Auto-Hardening ⭐NEW\n1387:## 详细修复指引 | Detailed Remediation Guide ⭐NEW\n1527:## 定期自动检查 | Periodic Auto-Check ⭐NEW\n1756:## 安全基线配置模板 | Security Baseline Templates ⭐NEW\n1970:## Python/Shell 脚本支持 | Scripting Support ⭐NEW\n2247:## 安全评分\n2251:## CVE 检查\n2255:## 容器安全\n2259:## 建议\n2321:## NVD CVE API 集成 | NVD CVE Integration ⭐NEW\n2508:## NVD 实时推送告警 | NVD Real-time Alerts 🆕\n3057:## 结构化日志与错误告警 | Structured Logging & Error Alerts 🆕\n3582:## 单元测试框架 | Unit Testing Framework 🆕\n4033:## 配置导入导出 | Config Import/Export 🆕\n4255:## 批量报告生成 | Batch Report Generation 🆕\n4434:## 📊 汇总统计\n4441:## 🖥️ 主机详情\n4464:## 📈 趋势分析\n4473:## 📋 建议行动\n4734:## 适用边界与不适用场景 | Applicability and Limitations\n4757:## 🛡️ 安全小知识：文件权限 vs Memory访问权限\n4846:## 工具检查项清单 | Checklist"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777110147172},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要在\"🚀 快速上手 | Quick Start\"之前添加新增功能的文档，或者在\"定期自动检查\"部分之后添加。让我读取这部分内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionhkc3efaoa7kq1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1520,"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":650,"output":126,"cacheRead":63611,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64387,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777110147174,"responseId":"063bbf83ad3c9dd7df642730bf4d8244"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionhkc3efaoa7kq1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| 防火墙规则 | `sudo ufw default deny incoming` | 🟢 | 1分钟 |\n| 文件权限 | `chmod 600 ~/.openclaw/config.json` | 🟢 | 1分钟 |\n| API密钥加密 | `openclaw config encrypt-secrets` | 🟡 | 5分钟 |\n| 自动更新 | `openclaw config set update.auto true` | 🟢 | 1分钟 |\n\n---\n\n## 定期自动检查 | Periodic Auto-Check ⭐NEW\n\n### ⏰ 定时检查配置指南\n\n**方式一：使用OpenClaw内置cron**\n```bash\n# 每天凌晨2点执行快速安全检查\nopenclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"healthcheck:daily-quick\" \\\n  --schedule \"0 2 * * *\" \\\n  --payload \"帮我做快速安全检查\" \\\n  --notify\n\n# 每周日凌晨3点执行深度安全审计\nopenclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"healthcheck:weekly-deep\" \\\n  --schedule \"0 3 * * 0\" \\\n  --payload \"帮我做完整安全审计并生成详细报告\" \\\n  --notify\n\n# 每月1号凌晨4点执行合规检查\nopenclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"healthcheck:monthly-compliance\" \\\n  --schedule \"0 4 1 * *\" \\\n  --payload \"帮我做合规性检查并生成报告\" \\\n  --notify\n```\n\n**方式二：使用系统cron + 脚本**\n\n本工具提供以下脚本支持定时检查：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 自动化修复脚本 - 检查并修复安全问题\n./scripts/auto-fixer.sh -c          # 仅检查\n./scripts/auto-fixer.sh -f          # 自动修复\n./scripts/auto-fixer.sh -r          # 生成详细报告\n\n# 2. 一键加固脚本 - 交互式加固\n./scripts/one-click-hardening.sh    # 交互式\n./scripts/one-click-hardening.sh -y # 自动确认\n\n# 3. 记忆文件审计 - 检查敏感数据\n\n[5583 more lines in file. Use offset=1570 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777110150698},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要在定期自动检查部分添加新的脚本说明。让我修改那部分。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctiondg3ax15z8cyx1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"```bash\n# 1. 自动化修复脚本 - 检查并修复安全问题\n./scripts/auto-fixer.sh -c          # 仅检查\n./scripts/auto-fixer.sh -f          # 自动修复\n./scripts/auto-fixer.sh -r          # 生成详细报告\n\n# 2. 一键加固脚本 - 交互式加固\n./scripts/one-click-hardening.sh    # 交互式\n./scripts/one-click-hardening.sh -y # 自动确认\n\n# 3. 增强版自动修复脚本 - v4.9.0 新增 ⭐\n./scripts/auto-fixer-v2.sh --risk-level safe      # 仅修复明确安全项\n./scripts/auto-fixer-v2.sh --risk-level standard  # 修复低风险项\n./scripts/auto-fixer-v2.sh --risk-level high      # 修复中风险项（需确认）\n./scripts/auto-fixer-v2.sh --rollback --backup=TIMESTAMP  # 回滚操作\n\n# 4. 极简模式 - v4.9.0 新增 ⭐\n./scripts/quick-detect.sh           # 自动探测环境\n./scripts/quick-detect.sh --quick   # 快速检查\n./scripts/quick-detect.sh --full    # 完整检查\n\n# 5. 中文向导 - v4.9.0 新增 ⭐\n./scripts/wizard.sh                 # 启动中文对话向导\n\n# 6. 定时巡检管理 - v4.9.0 新增 ⭐\n./scripts/cron-manager.sh --cron \"0 2 * * *\"    # 设置每日巡检\n./scripts/cron-manager.sh --cron list           # 查看已配置的定时任务\n./scripts/cron-manager.sh --cron remove        # 删除定时任务\n./scripts/cron-manager.sh --cron \"0 2 * * *\" --notify  # 发送巡检结果到飞书\n\n# 7. 记忆文件审计 - 检查敏感数据","oldText":"```bash\n# 1. 自动化修复脚本 - 检查并修复安全问题\n./scripts/auto-fixer.sh -c          # 仅检查\n./scripts/auto-fixer.sh -f          # 自动修复\n./scripts/auto-fixer.sh -r          # 生成详细报告\n\n# 2. 一键加固脚本 - 交互式加固\n./scripts/one-click-hardening.sh    # 交互式\n./scripts/one-click-hardening.sh -y # 自动确认\n\n# 3. 记忆文件审计 - 检查敏感数据"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":760,"output":646,"cacheRead":64059,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65465,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777110150700,"responseId":"063bbf8724e7b4178072043ac37127db"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctiondg3ax15z8cyx1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777110160352},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在需要更新 SKILL.md 的版本号，然后验证4个脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在更新版本号并验证脚本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionmedqqcg1revo1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -i 's/^version: 4.7.4$/version: 4.9.0/' /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionmedqqcg1revo2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && \\\necho \"=== 1. quick-detect.sh 语法检查 ===\" && \\\nbash -n scripts/quick-detect.sh && echo \"✅ 通过\" && \\\necho \"\" && \\\necho \"=== 2. wizard.sh 语法检查 ===\" && \\\nbash -n scripts/wizard.sh && echo \"✅ 通过\" && \\\necho \"\" && \\\necho \"=== 3. auto-fixer-v2.sh 语法检查 ===\" && \\\nbash -n scripts/auto-fixer-v2.sh && echo \"✅ 通过\" && \\\ne