\n\\033[1m常用 Cron 表达式:\\033[0m\n  0 2 * * *       每天凌晨 2:00\n  0 */4 * * *     每 4 小时\n  0 9 * * 1-5     工作日 9:00\n  0 2 * * 0       每周日 2:00"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777110184779},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"所有4个脚本验证完成。让我生成验证报告给用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionubjyqxvq1nae1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && \\\necho \"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\" && \\\necho \"【补充验证】auto-fixer-v2.sh --list-backups\" && \\\necho \"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\" && \\\nbash scripts/auto-fixer-v2.sh --list-backups 2>&1 | head -20","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":883,"output":138,"cacheRead":68091,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69112,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777110184782,"responseId":"063bbfa9341fe06efc5ea5711b251e41"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionubjyqxvq1nae1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n【补充验证】auto-fixer-v2.sh --list-backups\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n  [0;36m可用备份列表：[0m\n\n  暂无备份"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777110188884},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，所有验证完成了。现在我来汇总验证报告。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ v4.9.0 验证完成\n\n**版本已更新**: 4.7.4 → **4.9.0**\n\n---\n\n### 📋 验证结果\n\n| # | 脚本 | 语法 | 功能 | 状态 |\n|---|------|------|------|------|\n| 1 | `quick-detect.sh` | ✅ | 自动探测 OS/网络/服务/OpenClaw | ✅ 通过 |\n| 2 | `wizard.sh` | ✅ | 中文交互式向导（3步引导） | ✅ 通过 |\n| 3 | `auto-fixer-v2.sh` | ✅ | 分级修复（safe/standard/high）+ 回滚 | ✅ 通过 |\n| 4 | `cron-manager.sh` | ✅ | 定时巡检 + 飞书通知 | ✅ 通过 |\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 功能验证详情\n\n**1. quick-detect.sh**\n```\n检测到: Ubuntu 24.04 / 虚拟机环境 / OpenClaw 运行中\n安全评分: 75/100\n```\n\n**2. wizard.sh**\n```\n第1步: 选择机器类型 ✅\n第2步: 选择使用者范围 ✅\n第3步: 选择检查深度 ✅\n```\n\n**3. auto-fixer-v2.sh**\n```\n支持级别: --risk-level [safe/standard/high]\n备份管理: --list-backups ✅ / --rollback ✅\n```\n\n**4. cron-manager.sh**\n```\n支持操作: --cron [表达式/list/remove/status]\n支持选项: --notify / --summary\n```\n\n---\n\n**SKILL.md 已同步更新**，包含 4 个新功能的使用文档。\n\n请确认是否需要修改或发布？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":168,"output":370,"cacheRead":68987,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69525,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777110188885,"responseId":"063bbfad8b4a172d9797ae50cee5ce0d"},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51fc922630b0b4a876d71cc6174\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 17:47 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51fc922630b0b4a876d71cc6174]\nhaidong: 好的，发布的虾评，然后保存版本号一致再发布的GitHub"}],"timestamp":1777110480324},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求：\n1. 发布到虾评平台\n2. 保持版本号一致\n3. 发布到 GitHub\n\n让我按照 MEMORY.md 中的流程执行：\n1. 先上传到虾评获取版本号\n2. 同步版本号到本地 SKILL.md\n3. 提交到 GitHub 并打 tag","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kfdoujo7yqxs_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && \\\n# 1. 打包 ZIP\nzip -r healthcheck-v4.9.0.zip . -x \"*.git*\" -x \"*.zip\" -x \"*.tar.gz\" -x \"node_modules/*\" && \\\necho \"ZIP 已生成: $(ls -lh healthcheck-v4.9.0.zip | awk '{print $5}')\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":69349,"out