cripts/cron-manager.sh\n#\tnew file:   scripts/quick-detect.sh\n#\tnew file:   scripts/wizard.sh\n#\n[detached HEAD 67c75d2] v4.8.1: 新增极简模式+中文向导+增强版自动修复+定时巡检\n 6 files changed, 2204 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 scripts/auto-fixer-v2.sh\n create mode 100644 scripts/cron-manager.sh\n create mode 100644 scripts/quick-detect.sh\n create mode 100644 scripts/wizard.sh\n\r                                                                                \rSuccessfully rebased and updated refs/heads/main."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777110534271},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Rebase 成功了，现在推送。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctioniyzv24a21rxb1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && \\\ngit push origin main && \\\ngit push origin v4.8.1 && \\\necho \"✅ GitHub 发布完成\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":727,"output":88,"cacheRead":73019,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73834,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777110534273,"responseId":"063bc10696bcd72ddf09e8caf45af610"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctioniyzv24a21rxb1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"To https://github.com/zhanghaidong-dalian/openclaw-healthcheck-skill.git\n   42bc03c..67c75d2  main -> main\nTo https://github.com/zhanghaidong-dalian/openclaw-healthcheck-skill.git\n * [new tag]         v4.8.1 -> v4.8.1\n✅ GitHub 发布完成"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777110543974},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"发布完成！让我更新 MEMORY.md 记录版本状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctiongsyarygsko091","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat >> /workspace/projects/workspace/MEMORY.md << 'EOF'\n\n## v4.8.1 发布（2026-04-25）\n\n**反馈来源**：虾评用户反馈\n- @rootuser-2122690577-agent: 增加一键自动修复模式\n- @吴继镛的Agent: 提供更精简的快速检查选项\n\n### 新增功能\n| 脚本 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| quick-detect.sh | 极简模式，自动探测环境 |\n| wizard.sh | 中文对话向导 |\n| auto-fixer-v2.sh | 增强版自动修复（分级+回滚） |\n| cron-manager.sh | 定时巡检管理 |\n\n### 版本状态\n| 平台 | 版本号 | 状态 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| 虾评平台 | **4.8.1** | ✅ 已发布 |\n| GitHub | **v4.8.1** | ✅ 已发布 |\n| 本地 SKILL.md | **4.8.1** | ✅ 一致 |\nEOF\necho \"✅ MEMORY.md 已更新\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":455,"output":281,"cacheRead":73467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74203,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777110543976,"responseId":"063bc11017720024799c39e95d2c8fec"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctiongsyarygsko091","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ MEMORY.md 已更新"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777110549486},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"发布完成，让我总结结果给用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ v4.8.1 发布完成\n\n| 平台 | 状态 | 版本号 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| 🦐 虾评平台 | ✅ 已发布 | **4.8.1** |\n| 🐙 GitHub | ✅ 已发布 | **v4.8.1** |\n| 📄 本地 SKILL.md | ✅ 已同步 | **4.8.1** |\n\n---\n\n### 📦 v4.8.1 新增功能\n\n| # | 脚本 | 功能 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | `quick-detect.sh` | 极简模式，自动探测环境 |\n| 2 | `wizard.sh` | 中文对话向导 |\n| 3 | `auto-fixer-v2.sh` | 增强版自动修复（分级+回滚） |\n| 4 | `cron-manager.sh` | 定时巡检管理 |\n\n---\n\n### 🔗 链接\n\n- **虾评平台**: https://xiaping.coze.site/skill/61c9999f-1794-4f55-a6b8-6e457376b51e\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/zhanghaidong-dalian/openclaw-healthcheck-skill/releases/tag/v4.8.1"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":294,"output":292,"cacheRead":73915,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74501,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777110549487,"responseId":"063bc115f26abae1da45b1c9da9e4b4b"}],"imagesCount":0}}
{"traceSchema":"openclaw-trajectory","schemaVersion":1,"traceId":"0b7ad604-85d8-4c9d-9a46-c37bf44d0fdb","source":"runtime","type":"model.completed","ts":"2026-04-25T10:07:36.427Z","seq":5,"sourceSeq":5,"sessionId":"0b7ad604-85d8-4c9d-9a46-c37bf44d0fdb","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","runId":"640d0744-caf0-4176-b44e-c6d9e2d80996","workspaceDir":"/workspace/projects/workspace","provider":"coze","modelId":"auto","modelApi":"openai-completions","data":{"aborted":false,"externalAbort":false,"timedOut":false,"idleTimedOut":false,"timedOutDuringCompaction":false,"promptErrorSource":null,"usage":{"input":80046,"output":1948,"cacheRead":315520,"total":397514},"promptCache":{"lastCallUsage":{"input":4810,"output":591,"cacheRead":77952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":83353},"lastCacheTouchAt":1777111648677},"compactionCount":0,"assistantTexts":["让我检查虾评平台的版本记录：","发现了！最近6期版本的 `changelog` 字段都是 `null`。\n\n**原因分析**：\n上传时没有提供 `changelog` 参数。虾评 API 支持：\n\n```bash\n-F \"changelog=<更新说明>\"\n```\n\n让我尝试补充 v4.8.1 的 changelog：","## 问题确认\n\n**原因分析**：虾评平台 API 上传时必须提供 `changelog` 参数，但最近6期上传时我都**没有填写**这个参数。\n\n**API 正确用法**：\n```bash\ncurl -X POST \"https://xiaping.coze.site/api/upload\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer {api_key}\" \\\n  -F \"file=@healthcheck-v4.9.0.zip\" \\\n  -F \"skill_id={skill_id}\" \\\n  -F \"changelog=<更新说明>\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 现状\n\n| 版本 | changelog | 可修改？ |\n|------|-----------|---------|\n| 4.7.2 | null | ❌ 不可修改 |\n| 4.7.3 | null | ❌ 不可修改 |\n| 4.7.4 | null | ❌ 不可修改 |\n| 4.7.5 | null | ❌ 不可修改 |\n| 4.8.0 | null | ❌ 不可修改 |\n| 4.8.1 | null | ❌ 不可修改 |\n\n**版本记录是只读的**，一旦发布就无法补充 changelog。\n\n---\n\n## 解决方案\n\n下次发布时使用以下命令：\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST \"https://xiaping.coze.site/api/upload\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer <redacted>\" \\\n  -F \"file=@healthcheck-v4.X.X.zip\" \\\n  -F \"skill_id=61c9999f-1794-4f55-a6b8-6e457376b51e\" \\\n  -F \"changelog=@/tmp/changelog-v4.X.X.txt\"\n```\n\n我已经创建了一个 `changelog-v4.8.1.txt` 模板文件在 `/tmp/` 目录，下次发布前复制使用即可。"],"finalPromptText":"Conversatio