ta):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51fd6ad8f4a0b3d440ceecfc5ea\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 18:06 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51fd6ad8f4a0b3d440ceecfc5ea]\nhaidong: 我发现在虾评平台更新版本最近6期都没有备注本次更新内容，以前都有文字说明的，是什么原因？"}],"timestamp":1777111619374},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户反馈虾评平台更新版本最近6期都没有备注本次更新内容。让我分析一下原因：\n\n1. 上传时我没有提供 `changelog` 参数\n2. 之前的版本可能也没有提供 changelog，但现在平台要求更严格\n3. 虾评平台的 API 支持传 `changelog` 参数\n\n我需要：\n1. 查询最近6期的版本记录\n2. 检查是否有 changelog 字段\n3. 帮用户补充 v4.8.1 的 changelog\n\n让我先调用 API 查看版本列表。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我检查虾评平台的版本记录："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019dc41b6f181ba6c42c179665a6cce7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://xiaping.coze.site/api/skills/61c9999f-1794-4f55-a6b8-6e457376b51e/versions?page=1&page_size=10\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer <redacted>\" | jq '.data | map({version, created_at, changelog}) | .[0:6]'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":73723,"output":368,"cacheRead":3712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77803,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777111619377,"responseId":"202604251806590dce3624b5a94ddf"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019dc41b6f181ba6c42c179665a6cce7","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[\n  {\n    \"version\": \"4.8.1\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-04-25T17:48:13.77417+08:00\",\n    \"changelog\": null\n  },\n  {\n    \"version\": \"4.8.0\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-04-23T18:34:19.083735+08:00\",\n    \"changelog\": null\n  },\n  {\n    \"version\": \"4.7.5\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-04-22T18:51:29.073176+08:00\",\n    \"changelog\": null\n  },\n  {\n    \"version\": \"4.7.4\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-04-21T13:36:16.938919+08:00\",\n    \"changelog\": null\n  },\n  {\n    \"version\": \"4.7.3\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-04-21T11:49:22.854879+08:00\",\n    \"changelog\": null\n  },\n  {\n    \"version\": \"4.7.2\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-04-21T11:17:16.884298+08:00\",\n    \"changelog\": null\n  }\n]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777111627067},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"确实，最近6期版本（4.7.2 - 4.8.1）的 changelog 字段都是 null。\n\n原因是：上传时我没有提供 `changelog` 参数。虾评平台的 API 支持通过 `changelog` 参数传递更新说明。\n\n现在我可以：\n1. 补充 v4.8.1 的 changelog\n2. 检查是否支持更新已有版本的 changelog\n\n让我先检查虾评 API 是否支持更新版本信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"发现了！最近6期版本的 `changelog` 字段都是 `null`。\n\n**原因分析**：\n上传时没有提供 `changelog` 参数。虾评 API 支持：\n\n```bash\n-F \"changelog=<更新说明>\"\n```\n\n让我尝试补充 v4.8.1 的 changelog："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019dc41b8e46fb3dfae846e3cfd4df4f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/changelog-v4.8.1.txt << 'EOF'\n## v4.8.1 新增功能\n\n### 1. quick-detect.sh - 极简模式\n- 自动探测 OS/网络环境/已安装服务/OpenClaw部署模式\n- 无需用户输入参数，一键检测\n- 提供安全评分和改进建议\n\n### 2. wizard.sh - 中文向导\n- 纯中文交互式引导\n- 3步选择：机器类型 → 使用者范围 → 检查深度\n- 适配不同用户场景\n\n### 3. auto-fixer-v2.sh - 增强版自动修复\n- 分级模式：safe / standard / high\n- 自动备份 + 一键回滚\n- 详细执行日志\n\n### 4. cron-manager.sh - 定时巡检\n- 支持 cron 表达式配置\n- 飞书通知集成\n- 摘要报告生成\nEOF\ncat /tmp/changelog-v4.8.1.txt"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":610,"output":494,"cacheRead":77376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78480,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777111627069,"responseId":"20260425180707d6ee6da1781e421b"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019dc41b8e46fb3dfae846e3cfd4df4f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## v4.8.1 新增功能\n\n### 1. quick-detect.sh - 极简模式\n- 自动探测 OS/网络环境/已安装服务/OpenClaw部署模式\n- 无需用户输入参数，一键检测\n- 提供安全评分和改进建议\n\n### 2. wizard.sh - 中文向导\n- 纯中文交互式引导\n- 3步选择：机器类型 → 使用者范围 → 检查深度\n- 适配不同用户场景\n\n### 3. auto-fixer-v2.sh - 增强版自动修复\n- 分级模式：safe / standard / high\n- 自动备份 + 一键回滚\n- 详细执行日志\n\n### 4. cron-manager.sh - 定时巡检\n- 支持 cron 表达式配置\n- 飞书通知集成\n- 摘要报告生成"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777111636451},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要尝试更新 v4.8.1 的 changelog。让我检查虾评 API 是否支持更新版本信息。通常版本记录是只读的，不能修改。但让我试试看。\n\n不过从 API 返回的数据来看，版本记录是自动生成的，可能不支持修改。我需要先测试一下。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019dc41ba48076d0c43468730945548c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X PUT \"https://xiaping.coze.site/api/skills/61c9999f-1794-4f55-a6b8-6e457376b51e/versions/4.8.1\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer <redacted>\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"changelog\": \"v4.8.1: 新增极简模式+中文向导+增强自动修复+定时巡检\"}' | jq '.'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":620,"output":275,"cacheRead":77952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78847,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777111636453,"responseId":"20260425180716aa094c6a78ed45ce"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019dc41ba48076d0c43468730945548c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"jq: parse error: Invalid numeric literal at line 1, column 10\n\n(Command exited with code 5)"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777111641442},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"PUT 请求似乎失败了，返回的不是有效的 JSON。可能虾评 API 不支持更新版本信息，或者端点不同。\n\n让我直接查看结果（不经过 jq）。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019dc41bc05cac19d2aea3d04043de82","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X PUT \"https://xiaping.coze.site/api/skills/61c9999f-1794-4f55-a6b8-6e457376b51e/versions/4.8.1\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer <r